      "content": "wait vitamin b12 for breathing?? lol. i don't think i have any bronchodilator spray at home though. i just have some zyrtec and some extra strength ibuprofen. would it be okay if i just took a few of those instead to clear my chest up? i really don't want to have to go to the doctor if it's just allergies.",
